{"word":"σακκίον","slug":"σακκίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σακκίον</b></el> <el>(σακκίον, <el>attic</el> <el>σᾰκίον, ου, τό</el>,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:σάκκος'><el>σάκκος</el></a> or <el>σάκος</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a small bag</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>sackcloth, mourning</i>, Menand.<p/></div>"}]}